@startuml
[*] --> Order
Order --> Arrival : plane acquired
Arrival --> Preparation : arrival
Preparation --> Operations : condition and schedule allow
Operations --> [*] : scheduled flights remain
Operations --> Maintenance : no more scheduled flights or maintenance required
Maintenance --> Preparation : checked and serviced
Preparation --> Operations : ready for operations
Preparation --> [*] : plane taken out of service
Order --> [*] : plane permanently withdrawn from service
@enduml
